WEBVTT

00:00:35.890 --> 00:00:38.640
=Angels and Guards=

00:00:38.640 --> 00:00:41.180
=Episode 13=

00:00:41.390 --> 00:00:42.970
(Emerald Pavilion)

00:00:45.770 --> 00:00:49.520
(Magnanimous and Refined)

00:00:59.083 --> 00:00:59.500
Bingfan.

00:01:01.041 --> 00:01:01.583
Guan.

00:01:02.416 --> 00:01:03.166
This is a remedy

00:01:03.500 --> 00:01:05.250
I asked someone to find
for your insomnia.

00:01:06.833 --> 00:01:07.791
I... I brewed it myself.

00:01:09.666 --> 00:01:10.250
This

00:01:10.583 --> 00:01:12.708
uses pork heart with 15 grams
of biota seeds,

00:01:13.208 --> 00:01:16.458
(Magnanimous and Refined)
seasoned with various spices and lard.

00:01:18.083 --> 00:01:19.416
Once the pork heart is cooked,

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:20.708
take one serving a day,

00:01:21.291 --> 00:01:22.333
and you will sleep peacefully

00:01:23.000 --> 00:01:23.791
without nightmares.

00:01:25.875 --> 00:01:26.333
Pork...

00:01:26.625 --> 00:01:27.208
Pork heart?

00:01:30.125 --> 00:01:30.875
It really works.

00:01:36.250 --> 00:01:36.583
Here.

00:01:36.625 --> 00:01:37.125
Drink it while it is hot.

00:01:37.333 --> 00:01:38.125
No, no.

00:01:38.166 --> 00:01:38.833
Guan,

00:01:38.833 --> 00:01:39.875
I appreciate the thought.

00:01:40.500 --> 00:01:41.791
But this pork heart...

00:01:42.125 --> 00:01:43.041
I brewed it myself.

00:01:43.916 --> 00:01:44.666
Try it.

00:01:45.833 --> 00:01:47.041
Have you tried it yourself?

00:01:54.708 --> 00:01:55.666
I don't have insomnia.

00:01:56.041 --> 00:01:56.791
Why would I drink it?

00:01:57.500 --> 00:01:58.166
Right, Bingfan?

00:02:01.625 --> 00:02:03.833
Then how do you know it works?

00:02:04.916 --> 00:02:05.291
I...

00:02:09.541 --> 00:02:10.083
I will try it.

00:02:13.083 --> 00:02:13.750
You are too precious for this.

00:02:14.458 --> 00:02:15.250
Let me try it myself.

00:02:37.708 --> 00:02:38.375
How does it taste?

00:02:53.416 --> 00:02:53.958
Bingfan.

00:02:54.416 --> 00:02:55.291
Thank goodness you didn't drink it.

00:03:07.208 --> 00:03:08.333
Please don't make it again.

00:03:12.833 --> 00:03:13.500
Bingfan,

00:03:14.291 --> 00:03:15.708
I'm good at cooking actually.

00:03:16.041 --> 00:03:16.958
I will make you something later.

00:03:23.875 --> 00:03:24.500
Archivist Li.

00:03:25.541 --> 00:03:28.708
May I access Commissioner Lu's
service record

00:03:29.041 --> 00:03:29.958
and the case files he handled?

00:03:30.166 --> 00:03:32.291
He holds the fourth rank.

00:03:32.666 --> 00:03:34.458
His files aren't classified internally.

00:03:35.166 --> 00:03:37.125
But why do you want to see

00:03:37.166 --> 00:03:39.666
his service record and case files?

00:03:40.166 --> 00:03:40.458
I...

00:03:43.541 --> 00:03:45.458
I greatly admire him.

00:03:47.708 --> 00:03:49.375
Archivist Li, please don't ask.

00:03:49.833 --> 00:03:50.708
Just tell me

00:03:51.000 --> 00:03:52.541
whether I have the rank and authority

00:03:52.791 --> 00:03:55.291
to access Commissioner Lu's
service record and case files.

00:03:56.583 --> 00:03:58.125
Of course you do, Chief Squad Leader.

00:03:58.708 --> 00:03:59.125
Here.

00:03:59.333 --> 00:04:00.083
Register here.

00:04:06.270 --> 00:04:08.720
(Chong'er Pavilion)

00:04:10.041 --> 00:04:11.541
Lu Guokai and Shen Lian received orders.

00:04:11.958 --> 00:04:14.791
A swift search was conducted, followed
by interrogation and investigation.

00:04:15.250 --> 00:04:16.541
The official site was then confirmed.

00:04:19.583 --> 00:04:21.000
So Lu Guokai

00:04:22.000 --> 00:04:23.750
used to be my father's partner.

00:04:25.958 --> 00:04:27.791
Before Prince Luo's treason case,

00:04:29.500 --> 00:04:30.750
his career was going nowhere.

00:04:31.083 --> 00:04:32.375
He had always ranked below my father,

00:04:32.958 --> 00:04:34.166
only a Deputy Qianhu.

00:04:35.083 --> 00:04:36.375
But after Prince Luo's case,

00:04:36.958 --> 00:04:38.166
he rose quickly

00:04:38.458 --> 00:04:39.500
and became the Commissioner.

00:04:40.625 --> 00:04:42.000
He became the only man

00:04:42.000 --> 00:04:43.958
Commander Zhang could rely on.

00:04:47.310 --> 00:04:51.640
(Jinyiwei Prison Case: Lu Guokai)

00:04:52.666 --> 00:04:53.375
Lu Guokai.

00:04:54.083 --> 00:04:55.583
Did you frame my father

00:04:56.708 --> 00:04:58.041
to rise through the ranks?

00:05:30.000 --> 00:05:31.750
Shen Bingfan wanted to see my files,

00:05:32.333 --> 00:05:33.250
and you let her?

00:05:33.708 --> 00:05:37.333
By regulation, as Chief Squad Leader,
she is qualified to access them.

00:05:37.916 --> 00:05:41.000
Besides, any files open for borrowing

00:05:41.500 --> 00:05:42.791
are safe to be seen.

00:05:43.083 --> 00:05:44.083
There are no flaws.

00:05:44.666 --> 00:05:45.500
Rest assured, my lord.

00:05:47.625 --> 00:05:49.208
What would I have to worry about?

00:05:50.875 --> 00:05:51.416
She said

00:05:52.291 --> 00:05:53.958
she greatly admires you.

00:05:59.750 --> 00:06:00.125
Enough.

00:06:00.625 --> 00:06:01.333
You may go.

00:06:02.791 --> 00:06:03.291
Yes, my lord.

00:06:10.083 --> 00:06:11.541
Shen Bingfan...

00:06:14.291 --> 00:06:16.291
Why is she investigating my record?

00:06:40.125 --> 00:06:40.625
Your Highness.

00:06:40.916 --> 00:06:42.333
A letter was left on the veranda.

00:06:43.375 --> 00:06:44.291
Why are you in such a panic?

00:06:44.291 --> 00:06:46.375
(In honor of Your Highness's
22nd birthday,)

00:06:46.875 --> 00:06:47.708
(on the day of your celebration,)

00:06:48.083 --> 00:06:49.250
(I shall come personally
to offer my wishes)

00:06:49.916 --> 00:06:51.041
(and borrow
the imperial Dragon-Phoenix Jade.)

00:06:51.041 --> 00:06:51.666
The phantom thief Feng Fuliu!

00:06:52.833 --> 00:06:54.125
(Respectfully, Feng Fuliu.)

00:07:04.458 --> 00:07:05.833
(Northern Bureau)
This Dragon-Phoenix Jade

00:07:06.291 --> 00:07:09.250
was bestowed by the late emperor
as Princess Pingyang's dowry.

00:07:09.625 --> 00:07:11.916
Feng Fuliu has shown contempt
for imperial authority.

00:07:12.625 --> 00:07:15.916
Princess Pingyang has filed a petition
before His Majesty.

00:07:16.750 --> 00:07:18.500
Even the Empress Dowager
has been alarmed.

00:07:19.458 --> 00:07:20.458
His Majesty is furious.

00:07:20.666 --> 00:07:21.875
The Cabinet has issued an order.

00:07:22.416 --> 00:07:23.000
The Jinyiwei

00:07:23.375 --> 00:07:24.250
will mobilize in full.

00:07:24.625 --> 00:07:25.875
We won't withdraw

00:07:26.958 --> 00:07:27.833
until Feng Fuliu is captured.

00:07:28.625 --> 00:07:30.166
Yes, my lord.

00:07:31.166 --> 00:07:31.875
But

00:07:32.916 --> 00:07:34.125
that is easier said

00:07:35.041 --> 00:07:37.708
than done.

00:07:38.416 --> 00:07:38.958
My lord.

00:07:39.291 --> 00:07:40.708
This Dragon-Phoenix Jade,

00:07:40.833 --> 00:07:42.458
where is it usually kept?

00:07:43.375 --> 00:07:44.708
The princess keeps it on her person.

00:07:44.708 --> 00:07:45.208
Then,

00:07:46.208 --> 00:07:47.000
the male Jinyiwei

00:07:47.500 --> 00:07:49.291
may not be very convenient.

00:07:49.500 --> 00:07:50.166
Exactly.

00:07:50.333 --> 00:07:53.375
I have decided to assign this mission
to the female Jinyiwei

00:07:53.541 --> 00:07:56.250
and let them guard the princess.

00:07:57.250 --> 00:07:59.000
We swear to protect the princess
with our lives.

00:08:01.250 --> 00:08:02.500
By the way, Guokai,

00:08:02.625 --> 00:08:04.583
at the banquet, protect the princess

00:08:04.958 --> 00:08:05.875
and secure the treasure.

00:08:07.041 --> 00:08:09.250
As for whether we catch Feng Fuliu,

00:08:09.541 --> 00:08:10.375
that is no longer important.

00:08:11.041 --> 00:08:11.500
Yes, my lord.

00:08:13.458 --> 00:08:15.250
At last, we have a mission
to catch Feng Fuliu.

00:08:16.291 --> 00:08:17.416
Didn't you hear

00:08:17.416 --> 00:08:19.208
the Commander's order?

00:08:19.666 --> 00:08:21.125
Catching the thief is secondary.

00:08:21.500 --> 00:08:23.500
Protecting the imperial treasure
comes first.

00:08:25.125 --> 00:08:26.875
Do you think handsome Feng...

00:08:28.500 --> 00:08:28.791
No.

00:08:28.916 --> 00:08:30.291
I mean, Feng Fuliu.

00:08:30.666 --> 00:08:32.458
Why does he always return the treasures

00:08:32.583 --> 00:08:33.875
after he steals them?

00:08:35.166 --> 00:08:36.125
Maybe

00:08:36.166 --> 00:08:37.541
he is looking for something.

00:08:38.500 --> 00:08:40.166
But what exactly it is,

00:08:40.750 --> 00:08:42.083
even he doesn't know.

00:08:43.208 --> 00:08:44.333
I don't care what his purpose is.

00:08:44.625 --> 00:08:45.875
Now that we have this chance,

00:08:46.500 --> 00:08:47.375
I must catch him

00:08:47.625 --> 00:08:48.791
and see who he really is.

00:08:48.791 --> 00:08:50.416
Don't celebrate too soon.

00:08:50.791 --> 00:08:52.625
Lu Guokai is in overall command
this time.

00:08:52.916 --> 00:08:55.000
When the time comes,
he will definitely give all the credit

00:08:55.083 --> 00:08:56.041
to the male Jinyiwei.

00:08:56.333 --> 00:08:59.291
We will probably just be decoration.

00:09:05.750 --> 00:09:07.000
Chief Squad Leader Shen.
Squad Leader Hua.

00:09:07.000 --> 00:09:07.500
Squad Leader Cheng.

00:09:08.375 --> 00:09:09.083
Commissioner Lu requests your presence.

00:09:09.250 --> 00:09:11.416
May I ask why you summoned us, my lord?

00:09:11.916 --> 00:09:12.666
We're supposed

00:09:12.958 --> 00:09:15.083
to set an inescapable trap
at the princess's manor

00:09:15.166 --> 00:09:16.125
to capture Feng Fuliu.

00:09:16.958 --> 00:09:19.166
I have a special mission

00:09:19.458 --> 00:09:20.666
for the three of you.

00:09:20.916 --> 00:09:21.750
Please give us your orders.

00:09:24.375 --> 00:09:27.291
The princess's manor has many women.

00:09:28.250 --> 00:09:29.958
And at the birthday banquet,

00:09:30.333 --> 00:09:32.000
the female family members
of court officials

00:09:32.458 --> 00:09:34.791
and titled ladies will all be there
to celebrate.

00:09:35.208 --> 00:09:36.166
The male Jinyiwei

00:09:36.250 --> 00:09:37.833
can only guard the perimeter.

00:09:38.666 --> 00:09:40.500
That leaves no one
by the princess's side.

00:09:41.750 --> 00:09:42.958
To avoid exposing your identities,

00:09:43.666 --> 00:09:45.000
I order the three of you

00:09:45.583 --> 00:09:47.375
to disguise yourselves
as the princess's maids

00:09:47.750 --> 00:09:48.833
and protect Princess Pingyang.

00:09:51.625 --> 00:09:52.458
Dress as maids?

00:09:52.708 --> 00:09:54.458
So we are not joining the arrest?

00:09:54.500 --> 00:09:57.208
So we are there to serve?

00:09:57.375 --> 00:09:57.708
Well...

00:09:58.000 --> 00:10:00.458
Your mission is to protect the princess.

00:10:00.750 --> 00:10:02.875
The arrest will be handled
by the male Jinyiwei.

00:10:03.125 --> 00:10:03.583
But...

00:10:03.583 --> 00:10:04.125
But what?

00:10:04.416 --> 00:10:06.916
In the Jinyiwei,
there is only obedience. No buts.

00:10:09.500 --> 00:10:10.958
They are so underhanded.

00:10:11.208 --> 00:10:12.416
They said we could join the case,

00:10:13.000 --> 00:10:15.500
but they are just making us
serve as maids.

00:10:15.750 --> 00:10:17.125
But with the three of us

00:10:17.208 --> 00:10:18.208
around the princess,

00:10:18.375 --> 00:10:20.250
Feng Fuliu probably won't
succeed easily.

00:10:20.875 --> 00:10:23.125
Come on, don't be mad.

00:10:23.500 --> 00:10:25.208
(Northern Bureau)
Lu Guokai will persuade the princess

00:10:25.208 --> 00:10:26.708
(Northern Bureau)
to hide the real Dragon-Phoenix Jade.

00:10:27.041 --> 00:10:27.875
When the time comes,

00:10:27.875 --> 00:10:29.583
he will deploy the male Jinyiwei
to trap Feng Fuliu.

00:10:30.000 --> 00:10:31.083
As for the three of us,

00:10:31.458 --> 00:10:32.583
we are just there to protect her.

00:10:33.666 --> 00:10:35.375
Undercover little maids, that's all.

00:10:37.083 --> 00:10:38.583
Bingfan, Hua, Xintian.

00:10:39.458 --> 00:10:40.541
Come on.

00:10:40.708 --> 00:10:42.041
When you greet us,

00:10:42.041 --> 00:10:44.166
could you put in a little effort?

00:10:44.375 --> 00:10:46.833
At least look us in the eye.

00:10:47.166 --> 00:10:47.625
Well...

00:10:47.875 --> 00:10:49.208
Don't speak. Wait a moment.

00:10:50.000 --> 00:10:50.416
Bingfan.

00:10:50.791 --> 00:10:51.541
What were you going to say?

00:10:52.041 --> 00:10:53.000
Guan, what brings you here?

00:10:53.250 --> 00:10:55.041
I heard you were ordered
to capture Feng Fuliu.

00:10:55.458 --> 00:10:56.583
I came to see

00:10:56.708 --> 00:10:57.375
if there is anything I can help with.

00:11:09.833 --> 00:11:11.125
Why the long faces?

00:11:12.375 --> 00:11:14.833
If Lu Guokai tells us not to join,

00:11:14.958 --> 00:11:16.375
does that mean we stop catching
the thief?

00:11:18.125 --> 00:11:20.458
Since when have we ever listened to him?

00:11:21.416 --> 00:11:22.458
You mean...

00:11:23.458 --> 00:11:23.958
Bingfan,

00:11:24.500 --> 00:11:26.333
we will be Princess Pingyang's
maids anyway.

00:11:26.666 --> 00:11:28.458
If we talk the princess into it,

00:11:28.583 --> 00:11:30.000
she will go

00:11:30.125 --> 00:11:30.916
wherever we want her to go.

00:11:34.458 --> 00:11:35.166
Right.

00:11:36.041 --> 00:11:37.083
What I was worried about

00:11:37.416 --> 00:11:38.750
is that I'm sure that fool Lu Guokai

00:11:38.750 --> 00:11:39.791
can't catch Feng Fuliu.

00:11:39.916 --> 00:11:41.041
So we need a backup plan.

00:11:41.333 --> 00:11:42.500
The credit for catching Feng Fuliu

00:11:43.125 --> 00:11:44.333
must belong to us female Jinyiwei.

00:11:45.083 --> 00:11:46.458
Now that is more like it.

00:11:46.708 --> 00:11:48.541
Where there is a will,
there is a way.

00:11:49.833 --> 00:11:50.375
Bingfan,

00:11:50.625 --> 00:11:52.458
I don't want Hero Feng to be caught,

00:11:52.833 --> 00:11:53.416
but

00:11:53.708 --> 00:11:54.958
I want you to be happy.

00:11:59.041 --> 00:12:01.583
Tomorrow, we should ask Xu Duoyu
to come too.

00:12:01.833 --> 00:12:04.000
Those strange little gadgets of his

00:12:04.166 --> 00:12:05.833
are exactly what we need
against Feng Fuliu.

00:12:07.708 --> 00:12:08.625
Then it's settled.

00:12:08.916 --> 00:12:10.541
No matter what Lu Guokai plans,

00:12:10.541 --> 00:12:11.958
we need a plan of our own.

00:12:12.750 --> 00:12:13.291
When the time comes,

00:12:14.041 --> 00:12:15.208
we can't let Feng Fuliu

00:12:15.208 --> 00:12:16.958
run wild in Princess Pingyang's manor.

00:12:25.970 --> 00:12:28.708
(Bright Moon, Clear Breeze)

00:12:28.708 --> 00:12:29.208
Young Master Chang.

00:12:31.500 --> 00:12:32.208
What brings you here?

00:12:34.500 --> 00:12:35.375
Bingfan and the others asked me

00:12:35.375 --> 00:12:36.500
to attend a top-secret meeting.

00:12:39.166 --> 00:12:40.708
What top-secret meeting?

00:12:43.666 --> 00:12:45.041
I'm not sure.

00:12:49.166 --> 00:12:51.875
Duoyu, come in.

00:12:53.083 --> 00:12:53.875
Coming.

00:12:55.125 --> 00:12:55.625
Young Master Chang.

00:12:56.375 --> 00:12:57.000
Excuse me.

00:13:28.125 --> 00:13:28.750
What kind

00:13:30.791 --> 00:13:33.291
of top-secret meeting are you having?

00:13:34.166 --> 00:13:35.958
Since it is top secret,

00:13:36.166 --> 00:13:37.416
not just anyone can join.

00:13:37.958 --> 00:13:39.625
It has to do with Feng Fuliu, right?

00:13:40.208 --> 00:13:41.125
What does that have to do with you?

00:13:44.083 --> 00:13:45.125
I'm going back to my room.

00:13:45.125 --> 00:13:46.583
You are not a government officer.

00:13:46.583 --> 00:13:47.291
You cannot join.

00:13:47.708 --> 00:13:49.083
I can't go back to my own room?

00:13:49.416 --> 00:13:49.833
Bingfan.

00:13:50.416 --> 00:13:51.083
Am I late?

00:13:51.375 --> 00:13:52.416
Guan, go on in.

00:13:57.208 --> 00:13:57.625
What?

00:13:57.625 --> 00:13:58.125
I...

00:14:00.458 --> 00:14:01.833
I can't enter my own room?

00:14:02.375 --> 00:14:03.541
He can go in, but I can't?

00:14:06.833 --> 00:14:08.166
Bingfan, he is playing with my bird.

00:14:08.500 --> 00:14:09.500
Stop playing with my bird.

00:14:10.083 --> 00:14:12.708
He is an eighth-rank constable
of the Ministry of Justice.

00:14:12.833 --> 00:14:13.750
What office or rank do you hold?

00:14:13.916 --> 00:14:14.583
I...

00:14:17.750 --> 00:14:19.083
You couldn't handle it.

00:14:21.291 --> 00:14:22.791
You won't let me join the meeting.

00:14:24.250 --> 00:14:26.208
That means you suspect me, doesn't it?

00:14:27.125 --> 00:14:28.791
Since you asked, yes.

00:14:29.708 --> 00:14:30.375
But

00:14:30.458 --> 00:14:32.000
I hope my suspicion is wrong.

00:14:32.291 --> 00:14:34.000
So don't make this harder for me.

00:14:37.458 --> 00:14:38.791
Fine. I won't go in.

00:14:39.875 --> 00:14:41.500
Just don't blame me
for leaking secrets

00:14:42.250 --> 00:14:43.291
when you fail to catch Feng Fuliu.

00:14:49.583 --> 00:14:50.583
Stop playing with my bird.

00:15:01.333 --> 00:15:01.750
Everyone,

00:15:01.833 --> 00:15:02.166
this

00:15:02.583 --> 00:15:04.666
is what I spent all night calculating.

00:15:04.666 --> 00:15:06.083
Feng Fuliu's likely theft route

00:15:06.458 --> 00:15:07.500
and his escape route.

00:15:07.833 --> 00:15:09.541
How did you calculate all that?

00:15:42.666 --> 00:15:43.625
Duoyu.

00:15:44.125 --> 00:15:46.041
You are a genius.

00:15:48.208 --> 00:15:49.375
Also,

00:15:49.375 --> 00:15:50.291
I figured out

00:15:50.541 --> 00:15:51.625
that Feng Fuliu

00:15:51.958 --> 00:15:54.458
never hurts anyone during his thefts.

00:15:55.250 --> 00:15:57.166
So his usual tricks

00:15:58.083 --> 00:15:59.666
are disguise and knockout incense.

00:16:00.250 --> 00:16:03.000
But his footwork is exceptional,
so he is hard to catch.

00:16:03.000 --> 00:16:04.791
When it comes to footwork,

00:16:05.750 --> 00:16:07.333
I have some confidence.

00:16:08.500 --> 00:16:10.291
But I can't beat him.

00:16:11.000 --> 00:16:12.458
He is too agile.

00:16:13.041 --> 00:16:15.375
My slingshot can't hit him either.

00:16:15.541 --> 00:16:16.041
So,

00:16:16.541 --> 00:16:18.416
we cannot give him a chance
to use his footwork.

00:16:19.083 --> 00:16:20.083
That is too hard.

00:16:20.958 --> 00:16:21.750
Among us,

00:16:22.041 --> 00:16:23.458
who can capture Feng Fuliu alive?

00:16:26.041 --> 00:16:26.500
Young Master Chang.

00:16:26.833 --> 00:16:27.416
Can Young Master Chang do it?

00:16:27.916 --> 00:16:28.750
We absolutely can't use him.

00:16:34.041 --> 00:16:34.791
Let me think.

00:16:35.333 --> 00:16:37.833
Is there some mechanism
that can restrain Feng Fuliu?

00:16:38.458 --> 00:16:40.125
Hua, if you were Feng Fuliu

00:16:40.333 --> 00:16:42.291
and had to steal the Dragon-Phoenix Jade

00:16:42.291 --> 00:16:43.250
under so many guards,

00:16:43.416 --> 00:16:44.125
what would you do?

00:16:44.375 --> 00:16:45.166
Me?

00:16:45.916 --> 00:16:49.125
I would create chaos
and strike in the confusion.

00:16:49.375 --> 00:16:50.333
That is what I thought.

00:16:51.833 --> 00:16:52.791
I will go to the Commander

00:16:53.458 --> 00:16:54.416
and ask him to place archers

00:16:54.416 --> 00:16:55.541
where Feng Fuliu

00:16:55.625 --> 00:16:56.375
might escape.

00:17:11.250 --> 00:17:11.750
Young Master Chang.

00:17:12.125 --> 00:17:12.750
Xintian.

00:17:13.375 --> 00:17:14.625
You have been getting better lately.

00:17:15.083 --> 00:17:16.458
Young Master Chang, don't tease me.

00:17:16.958 --> 00:17:17.750
I'm not teasing you.

00:17:17.958 --> 00:17:19.625
I have seen your progress.

00:17:22.416 --> 00:17:22.916
Keep practicing.

00:17:23.125 --> 00:17:23.500
Okay.

00:17:28.750 --> 00:17:30.541
Was that a meeting just now?

00:17:31.041 --> 00:17:31.333
Yes.

00:17:31.708 --> 00:17:33.291
I thought you would be attending too.

00:17:34.833 --> 00:17:36.666
Is it about catching Feng Fuliu?

00:17:41.708 --> 00:17:43.375
How did you know?

00:17:45.625 --> 00:17:47.375
Bingfan must have told you, right?

00:17:48.333 --> 00:17:49.791
Of course.

00:17:51.416 --> 00:17:52.083
But

00:17:53.166 --> 00:17:54.125
I'm a little worried.

00:17:54.833 --> 00:17:55.458
Feng Fuliu...

00:17:55.791 --> 00:17:56.625
Can he really be caught?

00:17:57.125 --> 00:17:57.916
Don't worry.

00:17:58.333 --> 00:18:00.166
We have made a perfect plan.

00:18:00.541 --> 00:18:01.750
But he is Feng Fuliu.

00:18:02.333 --> 00:18:03.291
Will your plan work?

00:18:04.916 --> 00:18:05.916
Our plan is

00:18:06.208 --> 00:18:07.916
to make him think he has won,

00:18:08.458 --> 00:18:09.583
then, while he is getting smug,

00:18:10.125 --> 00:18:12.125
take him down in one strike.

00:18:13.208 --> 00:18:14.833
How ruthless.

00:18:16.166 --> 00:18:17.375
What a sharp plan.

00:18:18.416 --> 00:18:19.458
What exactly is it?

00:18:20.416 --> 00:18:21.875
I'll tell you.

00:18:22.041 --> 00:18:23.166
You can't tell anyone else.

00:18:23.291 --> 00:18:24.416
Who would I tell?

00:18:24.791 --> 00:18:25.208
Tell me.

00:18:43.270 --> 00:18:46.440
♪Because you once entered my dreams♪

00:18:46.810 --> 00:18:50.190
♪Truth and illusion blur in wine♪

00:18:50.440 --> 00:18:53.440
♪My heart drifted lost♪

00:18:53.440 --> 00:18:56.850
♪Yet found you in the crowd♪

00:18:57.940 --> 00:19:01.150
♪My blood still burns
as the world surges♪

00:19:01.560 --> 00:19:04.900
♪The land is fair, and you are free♪

00:19:05.480 --> 00:19:07.690
♪Sword drawn, lost in obsession♪

00:19:07.690 --> 00:19:11.730
♪I've softly let it go♪

00:19:11.730 --> 00:19:15.600
♪The vow you made was true♪

00:19:15.600 --> 00:19:19.350
♪Yet like clouds, it stops for no one♪

00:19:19.650 --> 00:19:21.560
♪Put away those dreamlike words♪

00:19:21.560 --> 00:19:26.100
♪And forget at world's end♪

00:19:26.400 --> 00:19:27.900
♪Embracing memory♪

00:19:27.900 --> 00:19:30.270
♪Through blossoms and dreams♪

00:19:30.270 --> 00:19:34.150
♪You hide in the crowd, silent♪

00:19:34.150 --> 00:19:36.480
♪I wish to let it pass♪

00:19:36.480 --> 00:19:41.480
♪And run toward this vast life♪